snippet.title: Destiny Child × Dead Or Alive Collaboration Trailer
snippet.description:
[Title]
Destiny Child X DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation Collaboration Trailer

[Description]
DESTINY CHILD x DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation COLLABO!
A festival of goddesses held on the Venus Islands!

Come and Meet your 'Destiny Child'.
http://global.destiny-child.com
https://moot.us/lounges/73/
https://www.facebook.com/DestinyChild.global/

Download now on Google play store, and App store

■ About DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation 
DEAD OR ALIVE Xtreme Venus Vacation (https://game.doaxvv.com/en/) is a spin-off title of Koei Tecmo Games' popular DEAD OR ALIVE series, featuring the series’ favorite characters enjoying tropical summer vacation staged on Venus Islands. (Available on Steam for Windows PC. Basic Free Play / Pay-Items via Steam Wallet) 

ⓒ LINE Games & SHIFT UP. All Rights Reserved.
ⓒ KOEI TECMO GAMES
